# Private analyst case notes. Keep the shared template versioned.
cases/*.md
!cases/case_template.md
!cases/INDEX.md

# output/ and data/ are intentionally versioned in public-demo mode because
# GitHub Pages and the daily workflow read them directly. For private
# operational deployments, stop committing generated reports/state and add:
# output/
# data/
# watchlist.txt
